## Warm Up

Warm Up:

3 rounds of: 10 squats, 10 sit ups, 10 push ups, 10 pull ups.

## WOD

WOD 26
All   levels:  run 1 mile OR bike 10 miles OR row 2000m for time.

## Cool Down

3 x 100m sprints.

## Post

Post time to comments.

